{"tid":1678540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可以點 到底可以點","createTime":"2019-10-27T16:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:30:17.000Z","uid":321198,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac11ab2b28a682fffeb34befb15fb30b31069ded","tid":1678540,"uid":321198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"(唔好推文回覆 推文宣post please)<br />\n發夢睇住手足比狗捕 乜都做唔到<br />\n返屋企對住藍屍父母 港豬朋友 冇人可以同我傾下<br />\n一個女仔 力又唔夠 跑又唔快 <br />\n望住手足狂嗌 冇拉到佢翻嚟<br />\n十年呀 我地冇拉到佢返嚟呀屌<br />\n而家瞓都瞓唔著 一合埋眼成個腦響住手足嗌救命既聲 <br />\n喊 冇撚用 但除咗喊我仲可以點"},{"pid":"841df155efaab10cd5a02b9d95248382abe34302","tid":1678540,"uid":336524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"「宣佈」政府若不在今個星期六之前宣佈成立獨立調查委員會調查警暴，我等將會行動升級。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678499</a><br />\n<br />\n升級係唯一出路"},{"pid":"1faf010091a6ae61940ab61e6738e708f77d372f","tid":1678540,"uid":198949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"就算唔夠力都好，至少都要練跑，唔好成為負累要班手足救自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d6e0ea62bcabfa413dc56b5606d962bfeb89d3","tid":1678540,"uid":321198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1faf010091a6ae61940ab61e6738e708f77d372f","tid":1678540,"uid":198949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"就算唔夠力都好，至少都要練跑，唔好成為負累要班手足救自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687c1bd59980be049fc4326a385f1c605fab299f","tid":1678540,"uid":110634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"本身我連遺書都draft埋，所有銀行密碼Fb ig ac都寫低哂，上前線前先俾和理非fd<br />\n有次舊患發作，好驚拖累到手足，自此之後就變咗和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3553437abe40f2ca35524410045f0d9db57105ce","tid":1678540,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=65ac198e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=f144e5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=6eed71ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"bb5c4643392d65955bc05894ee88710136e9bf7c","tid":1678540,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"我可以同你傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有意既再留TG"},{"pid":"ccdb3e6c4771c73fcfc4c7694fa422dd80d8c9fa","tid":1678540,"uid":321198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"687c1bd59980be049fc4326a385f1c605fab299f","tid":1678540,"uid":110634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"本身我連遺書都draft埋，所有銀行密碼Fb ig ac都寫低哂，上前線前先俾和理非fd<br />\n有次舊患發作，好驚拖累到手足，自此之後就變咗和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"我都講定囇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好明白你 勁驚拖累 唔出唔得 企得前又好似乜都做唔到 好灰<br />\n不過你有病歷就真係唔好太衝 做下文宣之類 小心身體啊"},{"pid":"302b08ce29bdd8ec1cf405a8fcd9cca132cc9bab","tid":1678540,"uid":321198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb5c4643392d65955bc05894ee88710136e9bf7c","tid":1678540,